location.fullValue: Aspen Plan, Arbor Collection at Bryson

data.description: Beautiful barely lived in 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 story home that is great for entertaining. This home sits on a nice sized corner lot(only 2 neighbors), and includes an open floor plan with an office down stairs as well as a small secondary living space upstairs that opens up to the beautiful views from the second story balcony. The garage also has a wet sink. Less than 4 miles from the Leander Train station, as well as groceries food and fun. This small pocket neighborhood is a great opportunity to settle your roots down in Leander, Tx. Seller is motivated and ready to move on.
